在[[幾何學|幾何學]]中，'''大二十面體'''是一種[[星形二十面體|星形二十面體]]，由20個正三角形組成，其在非凸均勻多面體被編號為U<sub>53</sub>、在溫尼爾多面體模型被編號為[[溫尼爾多面體模型列表|W]]<sub>41</sub>，是四種星形正多面體之一，[[對偶多面體|對偶多面體]]為[[大星形十二面體|大星形十二面體]]。

== 性質 ==
大二十面體共有20個面、30條邊和12個頂點<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.mathconsult.ch/static/unipoly/53.html|title=Uniform Polyhedra 53: great icosahedron|publisher=mathconsult.ch|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160325025133/http://www.mathconsult.ch/static/unipoly/53.html|archivedate=2016-03-25|access-date=2016-09-02|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web | url = http://bulatov.org/polyhedra/dual/ud57.html | title = great icosahedron | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160327152247/http://bulatov.org/polyhedra/dual/ud57.html | archivedate = 2016-03-27 | publisher = bulatov.org | access-date = 2016-09-02 | dead-url = no }}</ref>，20個面中，全部都是正三角形，且每個頂點都是5個三角形的公共頂點，但其以類似五角星的方式安排面的位置，使面互相相交，頂點圖為五角星，在[[施萊夫利符號|施萊夫利符號]]中可以用{3,5/2}來表示，而在{{link-en|考克斯特-迪肯符號|Coxeter-Dynkin digram|考克斯特符號}}中以{{CDD|node_1|3|node|5|rat|d2|node}}表示。

=== 頂點座標 ===
邊長為1位於原點大二十面體的頂點[[座標|座標]]為<ref name="dmccooeydata">{{Cite web | url = http://dmccooey.com/polyhedra/GreatIcosahedron.txt | title = Data of Great Icosahedron | publisher = dmccooey.com | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160902131144/http://dmccooey.com/polyhedra/GreatIcosahedron.txt | archivedate = 2016-09-02 | access-date = 2016-09-02 | dead-url = no }}</ref>：
:<math>( 0, \pm \frac{1}{2},  \pm \frac{\sqrt{5} - 1}{4})</math>
:<math>(\pm \frac{1}{2},  \pm \frac{\sqrt{5} - 1}{4},  0)</math>
:<math>( \pm \frac{\sqrt{5} - 1}{4},  0, \pm \frac{1}{2})</math>

=== 二面角 ===
大二十面體是一種[[正圖形|正圖形]]，因此其每個[[二面角|二面角]]都相等，皆為兩個正三角形的棱之交角，其值為五平方根的三分之一之[[反餘弦|反餘弦]]值<ref>{{cite web|url = http://dmccooey.com/polyhedra/GreatIcosahedron.html|title = Kepler-Poinsot Solids: Great Icosahedron|publisher = dmccooey.com|archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160324082606/http://dmccooey.com/polyhedra/GreatIcosahedron.html|archivedate = 2016-03-24|access-date = 2016-09-02|dead-url = no}}</ref>：
:<math>\cos^{-1} (\frac{\sqrt{5}}{3}) \approx 0.7297 \approx 41.8103 ^{\circ}</math>

